## Object

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`id` | `int` | Unique identifier
`name` | `string`
`category` | `int` | id of the [store category](/store-categories).  **expandable**
`address` | `hash` | Where the store is located
`address[line1]` | `string`
`address[line2]` | `string`
`address[line3]` | `string`
`address[zip_code]` | `string`
`address[city]` |`string`
`address[state]` |`string`
`address[country]` |`string`
`address[coords]` | `hash` |
`address[coords][lat]` | `number`
`address[coords][long]` | `number`
`photo` | `hash`
`photo[url]` | `string` | Absolute URL for the store photo.
`website` | `string` | URL of the stores website.
`tagline` | `string`
`distance` | `number` | Only used when listing stores and coords are provided.  The distance from the provided coords in miles.
`bounty` | `number` | How many bitcoins a hunter will receive for checking in at this store.

