## Retrieve

    GET /v1/stores/:id


## List

    GET /v1/stores

### Parameters

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | -----------
`coords` | `string` | Sort stores by distance from the coords.  Closest first. Format: lat,long. e.g. ?coords=12,34


## Store Bounty QR Code

    GET /v1/stores/:id/qrcode


